STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend House Bill No. 2125, page 6, line 5, by inserting after the period the following:
“Provided, however, an adjunct teacher employed to teach in an early childhood education program
shall be required to enroll in a State Department of Education approved training on the cognitive
science of how students learn to read during his or her first year of employment as an adjunct teacher
and complete the training by the end of his or her second year of employment as an adjunct teacher.
An adjunct teacher who fails to complete the training after two years of employment shall be
prohibited from teaching in an early childhood education program until the training has been
completed.”;
And, by amending the title to conform.
